{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/violet-evergarden-gaiden-film-indonesia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Violet Evergarden Gaiden Segera Tayang di Indonesia!","content":"\n<p>Masih segar di pikiran kita tentang <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/meluruskan-fakta-kebakaran-kyoto-animation/\">insiden kebakaran</a> yang menimpa studio anime Kyoto Animation. Kebakaran akibat aksi teror itu setidaknya menewaskan sekitar 34 orang, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"dengan 10 diantaranya (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-08-02/kyoto-police-release-names-of-10-victims-who-died-in-kyoto-animation-fire/.149629\" target=\"_blank\">dengan 10 diantaranya</a> dipastikan merupakan staf inti Kyoani yang menempati posisi sutradara, animator, dan posisi kunci lainnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Namun, direktur Kyoto Animation Hideaki Hatta memastikan bahwa studio animasi kebangaan kota Kyoto tersebut tidak akan berhenti menghasilkan karya terbaik mereka. Buktinya, film Violet Evergarden Gaiden yang tengah mereka garap akan segera rilis. Termasuk di Indonesia!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"45883\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/veronica-apakah-horor-netflix-paco-plaza-memang-benar-benar-bikin-jantung-mau-copot/attachment/eve5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dengan tangan mekanisnya, Violet menjadi Auto Memory Doll (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dengan tangan mekanisnya, Violet menjadi Auto Memory Doll (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5.jpg\" alt=\"Dengan tangan mekanisnya, Violet menjadi Auto Memory Doll (Sumber gambar: youtube.com)\" class=\"wp-image-45883\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/eve5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Dengan tangan mekanisnya, Violet menjadi Auto Memory Doll. (Sumber: youtube.com)</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk menyegarkan pikiranmu, <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-violet-evergarden-ketika-manusia-belajar-memahami-perasaan-sesamanya/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Violet Evergarden (opens in a new tab)\">Violet Evergarden</a> merupakan anime produksi Kyoto Animation yang menceritakan tentang sekelompok Auto Memories Doll, yaitu orang yang bekerja sebagai penulis surat. Violet Evergarden merupakan mantan tentara yang menghabiskan masa hidupnya di medan perang. Setelah perang berakhir, ia menjadi seorang Auto Memories Doll dan mengenal berbagai macam emosi yang belum pernah ia rasakan sepanjang hidupnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lWRXk7nOhsE\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Nah, di film Violet Evergarden Gaiden yang berjudul Eternity\nand the Auto Memories Doll ini, Violet ditempatkan di rumah keluarga besar York\nuntuk menjadi guru bagi penerus keluarga itu, Isabella York. Selama mengajari\nIsabella tentang tata krama, Violet menyadari bahwa Isabella merasa terpenjara\ndi rumahnya, tanpa bisa menentukan masa depannya sendiri.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55247\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/violet-evergarden-gaiden-film-indonesia/attachment/01-ve-gaiden/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ve-gaiden\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden.jpg\" alt=\"Isabella York menjadi tokoh sentral dalam Violet Evergarden Gaiden. Sumber: Comic Book\" class=\"wp-image-55247\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-ve-gaiden-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Isabella York menjadi tokoh sentral dalam Violet Evergarden Gaiden. Sumber: Comic Book</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Yui Ishikawa kembali memerankan Violet Evergarden, dengan\nMinako Kotobuki sebagai Isabella York dan Aoi Yuuki memerankan Taylor Bartlett,\nseorang anak yatim piatu. Pengisi suara lain dari anime Violet Evergarden: Aya\nEndo, Haruka Tomatsu, Kouki Uchiyama, Minori Chihara, dan Takehito Koyasu juga\nakan tampil di film spinoff ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Film Violet Evergarden Gaiden tayang perdana di Mannheim,\nJerman pada tanggal 3-4 Agustus lalu, dan akan tayang di Jepang selama 3 minggu\nmulai dari tanggal 6-26 September. Di Indonesia, Violet Evergarden Gaiden akan\ndiboyong oleh distributor film Feat Pictures, namun belum ada kepastian tanggal\ntayangnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55248\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/violet-evergarden-gaiden-film-indonesia/attachment/02-ve-gaiden/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ve-gaiden\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden.jpg\" alt=\"Violet mendengarkan keluh kesah Isabella. Sumber: Duniaku\" class=\"wp-image-55248\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-ve-gaiden-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Violet mendengarkan keluh kesah Isabella. Sumber: Duniaku</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meski demikian, mari kita nantikan kehadiran Violet Evergarden\nGaiden, karena tayangnya film Kyoto Animation di Indonesia merupakan momen yang\ncukup langka. Jika kesempatan itu muncul, tidak ada salahnya menunjukkan\ndukungan kepada Kyoto Animation yang tengah berusaha bangkit dari\nketerpurukannya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d1de0964-3c67-5163-a644-c061566670ae"}}}